title: Psychedelics & Success w/ Aubrey Marcus | The Expert Series
itunes:title: Psychedelics & Success w/ Aubrey Marcus | The Expert Series
description:
Aubrey Marcus is the founder of Onnit, which he just sold to Unilever for a large undisclosed amount. In this episode, we talk about how to overcome childhood trauma and how he believes that his psychedelic journeys and his personal and spiritual development were actually some of the biggest keys to his success.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
